{
  "stem": "979.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't even remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It just was something unreal, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Were you in a Greek barracks, or it was just everyone mixed together?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With the Greeks?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were-- they put us in a barracks with who ever comes, you know, whether they're Greeks or Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They don't separate the Greeks or not.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After they separated us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that night-- so at 4 o'clock in the morning the whistle started.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH]-- the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH] were also prisoners, but that was their job-- to tell us to get up, because we have to go to work.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we were in quarantine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The say we're in quarantine for a couple of weeks-- I think, the new people who come.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it so happened they-- when we-- when they whistled, and we got dressed fast, we went outdoors.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's what they did every day for the whole time-- that at 4 o'clock, they count you, that you are outside.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they count.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There have to be so many people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And if one is missing, we punished.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Like we stayed over an hour or so till they find the person.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it's freezing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah-- in the morning-- very early at night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we says, that's what they do?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were all shaking and that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And even if-- if somebody didn't-- didn't get away, we still stayed for about 15, 20 minutes there until they count us and all that.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and then we go in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and also-- but that next day-- that-- that same day, we were supposed to stay in for two weeks-- I mean, except to go outside to count us.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it happened that that week, that day, they-- one of the girls who was working for the-- that was the worst job that was there.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
